{"TopicId":195928,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How do I set RCS to main throttle?","CreatedByName":"eee","CreatedById":202855,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-28T17:18:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"eee","CreatedById":202855,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-28T17:18:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIm making an Ares 1 and Starliner mix, I need help setting \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E to the main throttle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Draalo","CreatedById":158993,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-28T18:23:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst go to settings and activate \u0022advanced tweakables\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E you can rightclick the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E thrusters then and choose \u0022show actuation toogles\u0022, should look like:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022unknown.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/567596967253770260/737736030081253437/unknown.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSwitch on \u0022Force by Throttle\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E must be turned on when thrusters shall fire.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHint: if you deactivate yaw, pitch and roll the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E wont use the thrusters anymore - no waste of monopropellant if vessel is just reorientating but still full \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E capabilities when using IJKL for docking\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-07-28T18:24:18Z\u0022 title=\u002207/28/2020 06:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 28, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Draalo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"eee","CreatedById":202855,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-28T21:19:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-29T00:32:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223827446\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022195928\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221595960631\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158993\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Draalo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Draalo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\u0022\u003Cstrong\u003EFore\u003C/strong\u003E by Throttle\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice that d\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#202124;font-size:18px;\u0022\u003Eoes exactly what it says on the tin.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont color=\u0022#202124\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003EVery convenient for craft that have multiple possible control directions.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Draalo","CreatedById":158993,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-29T13:47:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, i took the 4way thrusters for the example pictures - yes, not optimal.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut there are monodirectional thrusters too \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI build leightweight ComSats all the time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHECS probecore, 3x static solar, RA2 antenna, one battery, smallest monoprop tank and a pair of monodirectional thrusters below.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVessel mass below 0.5to., has about 230m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EdV\u003C/abbr\u003E - enough for manouvering around Mun and Minmus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEasy to send 4 of them with one launch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"eee","CreatedById":202855,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-29T16:21:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223827869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022195928\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596030466\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158993\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Draalo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Draalo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHECS probecore, 3x static solar, RA2 antenna, one battery, smallest monoprop tank and a pair of monodirectional thrusters below.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVessel mass below 0.5to., has about 230m/s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EdV\u003C/abbr\u003E - enough for manouvering around Mun and Minmus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEasy to send 4 of them with one launch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTIME TO INVADE THE MUNS SECURITY\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}